divs: Sighting DetailsOn the corner of Rt 590 and finn swamp road a round lack object with a big white light in the center and red lights going around the side. No sound just hovering. Was about the size of four two story houses. A Four other cars were pulled over looking at it. After about 5 minutes you can hear planes coming from a distance and thats when I drove away. I have never seen anything like that in my life.
